        <title>Trailer Connection</title>
        <para>The 7-Way Trailer Socket connects tractor and trailer wiring for operation of stop, tail, turn and hazard
            signal lights and clearance lights with the following configurations:
        </para>
        <randlist type="bullet">
            <item>
                <para>At back of cab</para>
            </item>
            <item>
                <para>At back of sleeper box</para>
            </item>
            <item>
                <para>Frame mounted socket, tractor application</para>
            </item>
            <item>
                <para>Frame mounted socket, truck application with air brakes.</para>
            </item>
        </randlist>
    </svcproc>
